ActFisheries Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Pulp and Paper Effluent Regulations (Miscellaneous Program)
PrecisRegulations Amending the PULP AND PAPER EFFLUENT REGULATIONS, in order to improve clarity of the regulatory text by identifying a single authorization officer for each province and to improve the consistency in wording between the French and English versions of the regulatory text. The amendments address comments made by the Standing Joint Committee for the Scrutiny of Regulations.
